HEADWORD: Photozincography
<hw>Pho`to*zin*cog"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Photo-</ets> + <ets>zincography</ets>.]</ety> <def>A process,
